negotiated</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/ordered\"><code>ordered</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/protocol\"><code>protocol</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/readyState\"><code>readyState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/reliable\"><code>reliable</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/stream\"><code>stream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/close\"><code>close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/send\"><code>send()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/bufferedamountlow_event\"><code>bufferedamountlow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/close_event\"><code>close</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/closing_event\"><code>closing</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/message_event\"><code>message</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel/open_event\"><code>open</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a WebRTC</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>MediaDevices.getUserMedia()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/mediaDevices\"><code>Navigator.mediaDevices</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/RTCCertificate\"><code>RTCCertificate</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDTMFSender\"><code>RTCDTMFSender</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDTMFToneChangeEvent\"><code>RTCDTMFToneChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannelEvent\"><code>RTCDataChannelEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDtlsTransport\"><code>RTCDtlsTransport</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCErrorEvent\"><code>RTCErrorEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCIceCandidate\"><code>RTCIceCandidate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/RTCIceTransport\"><code>RTCIceTransport</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnectionIceErrorEvent\"><code>RTCPeerConnectionIceErrorEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnectionIceEvent\"><code>RTCPeerConnectionIceEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCRtpReceiver\"><code>RTCRtpReceiver</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCRtpSender\"><code>RTCRtpSender</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCRtpTransceiver\"><code>RTCRtpTransceiver</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCSctpTransport\"><code>RTCSctpTransport</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCSessionDescription\"><code>RTCSessionDescription</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCStatsReport\"><code>RTCStatsReport</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCTrackEvent\"><code>RTCTrackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>A interface RTCDataChannel representa um canal de rede que pode ser usado para transferências bidirecionais de dados arbitrários de ponto a ponto. Todo canal de dados está associado a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code></a>, e cada conexão de pares pode ter até um máximo teórico de 65,534 canais de dados (o limite real pode variar de navegador para navegador).</p>\n\n<p>Para criar um canal de dados e pedir a um ponto remoto para se juntar a você, chame os metodos&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code></a>'s&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection/createDataChannel\"><code>createDataChannel()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.&nbsp; O interlocutor que está sendo convidado a trocar dados recebe um evento <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Reference/Events/datachannel\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">datachannel</a></code> (que possui o tipo <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannelEvent\"><code>RTCDataChannelEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>) para informá-lo de que o canal de dados foi adicionado à conexão.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> pc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RTCPeerConnection</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createDataChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"my channel\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ndc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onmessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"received: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ndc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onopen</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"datachannel open\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ndc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclose</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"datachannel close\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webrtc-pc/#idl-def-RTCDataChannel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebRTC 1.0: Real-time Communication Between Browsers<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'RTCDataChannel' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidata a Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Especificação inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/22\" title=\"Released on 2013-06-25.\">22</a> (22) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>onbufferedamountlow</code></td>\n   <td>56</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>43</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>29</td>\n   <td>29</td>\n   <td>22.0 (22) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>onbufferedamountlow</code></td>\n   <td>56</td>\n   <td>56</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>43</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] A interface é chamada DataChannel e não RTCDataChannel no Firefox. No entanto, uma ligação foi implementada desde o Firefox 24 para que qualquer um dos nomes funcione.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\">WebRTC</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A interface RTCDataChannel representa um canal de rede que pode ser usado para transferências bidirecionais de dados arbitrários de ponto a ponto. Todo canal de dados está associado a RTCPeerConnection, e cada conexão de pares pode ter até um máximo teórico de 65,534 canais de dados (o limite real pode variar de navegador para navegador).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"RTCDataChannel","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"RTCDataChannel","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"RTCDataChannel","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/rtcdatachannel","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/rtcdatachannel/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel","title":"RTCDataChannel"}],"pageTitle":"RTCDataChannel - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}